article.linkText: Demings and Rainwater score 12 to lead Utah Tech over UT Rio Grande Valley 81-64
article.story: SAINT GEORGE, Utah -- — Aric Demings and Tennessee Rainwater both had 12 points in Utah Tech's 81-64 victory against UT Rio Grande Valley on Thursday night. Demings finished 5 of 6 from the field for the Trailblazers (8-13, 4-6 Western Athletic Conference). Rainwater shot 4 of 6 from the field and 3 for 6 from the line. Tanner Christensen, Jaylen Searles and Noah Gonsalves all had 11 points. JJ Howard led the Vaqueros (6-15, 2-8) in scoring, finishing with 19 points and three steals. CJ Booker added 19 points for UT Rio Grande Valley. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
